[SN]TITLE[SN]
What makes you happy?

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
It's the International Day of Happiness, and people around the world are celebrating what makes them happy.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
20 March 2017 Last updated at 16:45 GMT
Whether it's sunshine, cute animals, playing sports, or getting hugs from your family, today is the day to celebrate!
Some of you have been telling Newsround about what makes you smile...
